      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TUTA SUN (7) finds it hard to break through. Finished in the money last time though when third (20.37) at this track. Has never been out of the placings from three starts out of this box. Rates highly and will give a great sight. INSANE DANCER (2) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Out Of Austrian (20.52) in a Grade 4/5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Winning chance. NOAKI STAR (6) doesn't win out of turn. Finished third (20.24) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Has a good record here including five wins. Expected to feature again. TUSKEN WARRIOR (1) racing over this distance brings the best out in him.",
